{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"WAI-ARIA Roles","mdn_url":"/ru/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles","locale":"ru","native":"Русский","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p class=\"summary\">This page lists reference pages covering all the WAI-ARIA roles discussed on MDN. For a full list of roles, see <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques\">Using ARIA: Roles, States, and Properties</a></p>\n\n<p></p><dl><dt class=\"landingPageList\" id=\"aria_checkbox_role\"><a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/checkbox_role\">ARIA: checkbox role</a></dt><dd class=\"landingPageList\"><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/wai-aria-1.1/#checkbox\" rel=\" noopener\">checkbox role</a> используется для переключаемых интерактивных элементов управления. Элементы, содержащие&nbsp;<code>role=\"checkbox\"</code> также должны включать&nbsp;<code>aria-checked</code> атрибут, чтобы продемонстрировать состояние чекбокса ассистивным технологиям.</dd></dl><p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"This page lists reference pages covering all the WAI-ARIA roles discussed on MDN. For a full list of roles, see Using ARIA: Roles, States, and Properties","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WAI-ARIA Roles","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"WAI-ARIA ロール","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"WAI-ARIA Roles","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"WAI-ARIA Roles","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"WAI-ARIA Roles","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ru/web/accessibility/aria/roles","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ru/web/accessibility/aria/roles/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ru